Cell.Text: You've made a mess of things and Maven's furious. I told you not to burn more than three of the hives! | I've smoothed things over with her for now, but you can forget your cut.
Word on the street is Goldenglow's been hit. Good job, lad.
Word on the street is Goldenglow's been hit. Good job, lass.
Sorry. Here's what was in the safe.
[S] At least you remembered one of the things I asked. Let me see that.
[S] Let me take a look at what you found.

Node.Caption: TG02BrynjolfQuestDoneBranchTopic01: Yes, and here's what was in the safe.

Cell.Text: [S] Don't sound so eager, it's not a social visit. It's business.

Node.Caption: TG02BrynjolfQuestDoneBranchTopic01a: Good, it's about time I met her.

Cell.Text: [S] Oh, no. Nothing like that. You're calling on her for business.

Node.Caption: TG02BrynjolfQuestDoneBranchTopic01b: I thought I did the job like you asked...

Cell.Text: [S] Ha ha. If it was like that she wouldn't be asking for you, she'd be calling on the Dark Brotherhood. | It's just business.

Node.Caption: TG02BrynjolfQuestDoneBranchTopic01c: Sure, but will I come out of there alive?

Cell.Text: Aringoth sold Goldenglow? What's that idiot thinking? | He has no idea the extent of Maven's fury when she's been cut out of a deal, but I'm certain he'll find out. | If only this parchment had the buyer's name instead of this odd symbol. Any idea what that might be?

Node.Caption: TG02BrynjolfQuestDoneBranchTopic001a: So, what did you think about the deed?

Cell.Text: Blast. Well, I'll check my sources and speak to Mercer. | But for now, you're off to speak to Maven Black-Briar. She asked for you by name.
[S] G|That's between you and Maven and I prefer to keep it that way. | Just keep your ears open and your mouth shut and you'll do fine.
That's between you and Maven and I prefer to keep it that way. | Don't worry about it. Maven's business dealings usually involve quite a bit of gold for her people.

Node.Caption: TG02BrynjolfQuestDoneOutroBranchTopic: What does Maven want from me?

Cell.Text: [S] Of course... your pay. Haha! You're smart as a whip, lad. | Keep doing right by us and there's plenty more where that came from.
[S] Of course... your pay. Haha! You're smart as a whip, lass. | Keep doing right by us and there's plenty more where that came from.
